Currency Management Solution

Overview
This project deploys a Salesforce Currency Management solution. 
The solution will combine Salesforce with FreeCurrencyAPI to retrieve and update master currency information.

---

Architecture
•⁠  ⁠Lightning Web Component (LWC) of manual sync and data view.
•⁠  ⁠API call out and data processing apex.
•⁠  ⁠Signed Endpoint credentials in secure API access.
•⁠  ⁠Apex to be manually synchronized on a daily basis.
•⁠  ⁠Currency master data object
•⁠  ⁠Custom Object for currency master data

---

Functional Flow
1.⁠ ⁠The user clicks on Sync Currencies in LWC.
2.⁠ ⁠FreeCurrencyAPI is called by Apex as Named Credential.
3.⁠ ⁠Response has been mapped and converted to Currency__c.
4.⁠ ⁠UPSERTing of records is by means of external ID.
5.⁠ ⁠The information is presented in LWC datatable.
6.⁠ ⁠Apex Data is refreshed on a daily basis.

---

Components

Custom Object
•⁠  ⁠Currency__c
  - Currency_Code__c (External ID)
  - Symbol__c
  - Native_Symbol__c
  - Decimal_Digits__c
  - Rounding__c
  - Plural_Name__c

Apex Classes
•⁠  ⁠⁠ CurrencyApiService ⁠ - API callout/parsing.
•⁠  ⁠Currencycontroller - LWC + Scheduler interface.
•⁠  ⁠⁠ CurrencyScheduler ⁠ - Daily automatic synchronization.
•⁠  ⁠`CurrencyControllerTest- Mock callouts Test coverage.

Lightning Web Component
•⁠  ⁠⁠ currencyManager ⁠
  - Sync button
  - Currency datatable
  - Auto refresh by refreshApex

---

Security
•⁠  ⁠Named Credentials
•⁠  ⁠No API keys in Apex or LWC
•⁠  ⁠External ID based UPSERT

---

